   MODULE_PREFIX=${X11R7_PREFIX:-/usr/X11R7}
        WEB_SITE=http://www.x.org/
         ENTERED=20060302
         UPDATED=20060302
           SHORT="video driver for framebuffer device"

cat << EOF
fbdev is an __xservername__ driver for framebuffer devices. This is a
non-accelerated driver, the following framebuffer depths are supported: 8,
15, 16, 24. All visual types are supported for depth 8, and TrueColor visual
is supported for the other depths. Multi-head configurations are supported.
EOF
